Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Saskatchewan is pleased to offer 42.37 acres of highway fronting land adjacent to the bustling city of Warman, SK. As Saskatchewan’s newest and fastest growing city, Warman boasts a robust, young population of over 17 500 residents. Located just 10 kilometers north of Saskatoon, Warman continues to bean attractive location for both commercial and residential development. Services to the site include a water and sewer pipe running along the east side of the property, with power serviced to the site as well. Many great local bakeries, coffee shops, and restaurants are located within a few kilometers of the property.

CBRE Saskatchewan is pleased to offer 42.37 acres of highway fronting land adjacent to the bustling city of Warman, SK. As Saskatchewan’s newest and fastest growing city, Warman boasts a robust, young population of over 17,500 residents. Located just 10 kilometers north of Saskatoon, Warman continues to be an attractive location for both commercial and residential development. Services to the site include a water and sewer pipe running along the east side of the property, with power serviced to the site as well. Many great local bakeries, coffee shops, and restaurants are located within a few kilometers of the property.

This 3.9 acre parcel of land is zoned for multifamily housing and is located just off Centennial Boulevard in Warman, SK. The area is experiencing rapid development which will provide many amenities for future residents. These amenities include close proximity to a major grocer, home hardware store, and fast food restaurants.
